omainTopologySteps", "committedDate": "2020-03-18T00:35:17Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "edbf921cc0f1be9bfb96bc8b68e568d556f24d9f", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/edbf921cc0f1be9bfb96bc8b68e568d556f24d9f", "message": "display domain topology valiation warnings to domain status message", "committedDate": "2020-03-18T00:36:36Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "dc77511653d0806a1c445ca3e3d04e209a630312", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/dc77511653d0806a1c445ca3e3d04e209a630312", "message": "Merge branch 'develop' into owls-78058\n\nConflicts:\n\tdocs/charts/index.yaml\n\tdocs/charts/weblogic-operator-2.6.0.tgz\n\tkubernetes/crd/domain-crd.yaml", "committedDate": "2020-03-18T00:40:39Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "75bd9f0b40fd68d855dc4c7f1b8ce408a7f97941", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/75bd9f0b40fd68d855dc4c7f1b8ce408a7f97941", "message": "merge conflict", "committedDate": "2020-03-18T00:51:18Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "a9eddf9c1369f0eb97d68089a0cc1b27c8848a50", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/a9eddf9c1369f0eb97d68089a0cc1b27c8848a50", "message": "added more unit tests", "committedDate": "2020-03-18T23:18:36Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "3ce31b0864c455e583382d721f61a247cd82d521", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/3ce31b0864c455e583382d721f61a247cd82d521", "message": "Merge branch 'develop' into owls-78058", "committedDate": "2020-03-18T23:21:52Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "18e64727d1747eb544533476b633e27af8954008", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/18e64727d1747eb544533476b633e27af8954008", "message": "add missing desiredState in copy constructor. desiredState should not be required", "committedDate": "2020-03-20T17:52:54Z", "type": "commit"}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5NjM4Mjc3Ng==", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/pull/1484#discussion_r396382776", "bodyText": "Let's discuss the use of \"Required\" here.  I think it's okay because we are going to version 3.0.0, so there can be non-backward compatible changes. However, just having \"Required\" in the description doesn't make the field required.  If we want the field to be required in the schema, then tag the field with @nonnull.", "author": "rjeberhard", "createdAt": "2020-03-23T11:28:35Z", "path": "operator/src/main/java/oracle/kubernetes/weblogic/domain/model/ClusterStatus.java", "diffHunk": "@@ -38,6 +38,11 @@\n   @Range(minimum = 0)\n   private Integer maximumReplicas;\n \n+  /** The requested number of cluster members. Required. */\n+  @Description(\"The requested number of cluster members. Required.\")", "originalCommit": "18e64727d1747eb544533476b633e27af8954008", "replyToReviewId": null, "replies": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5NjUzMDA3NQ==", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/pull/1484#discussion_r396530075", "bodyText": "I don't think it should be required - seems too prescriptive. I suspect what Lenny really meant was that the default is 0, which surprises some folks.  How about something like \"The requested number of cluster members. Set above 0 (the default) to ensure cluster members start.\"?   Not sure if that's good wording, but maybe something like that?", "author": "tbarnes-us", "createdAt": "2020-03-23T15:18:37Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5NjM4Mjc3Ng=="}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5NjYxNTg3Mg==", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/pull/1484#discussion_r396615872", "bodyText": "Updated replicasGoal to:\n/** The requested number of cluster members from the domain spec. */\n@description(\"The requested number of cluster members from the domain spec. \"\n+ \"Cluster members will be started by the operator if this value is larger than zero.\")\n@range(minimum = 0)\nprivate Integer replicasGoal;", "author": "alai8", "createdAt": "2020-03-23T17:12:24Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM5NjM4Mjc3Ng=="}], "type": "inlineReview"}, {"oid": "a087e69d48d29fe83b0ffae6994e521f70cab66f", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/a087e69d48d29fe83b0ffae6994e521f70cab66f", "message": "Merge branch 'develop' into owls-78058-wip", "committedDate": "2020-03-23T16:03:26Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "126e65c532a44192a0efbd911910a9b8ba9b172c", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/126e65c532a44192a0efbd911910a9b8ba9b172c", "message": "clarify topology validation messages", "committedDate": "2020-03-23T16:23:17Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "dacc45de3f184a132c96d2e633a488664303277f", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/dacc45de3f184a132c96d2e633a488664303277f", "message": "replicasGoal should not be required", "committedDate": "2020-03-23T16:24:18Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "144ac476db77b0ce4dc52c03b485e07ca538d08d", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/144ac476db77b0ce4dc52c03b485e07ca538d08d", "message": "remove weblogic-operator-2.6.0.tgz from branch", "committedDate": "2020-03-23T16:32:20Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "d1f45b783d7b5951f84f14a2daf9a7f326312482", "url": "https://github.com/oracle/weblogic-kubernetes-operator/commit/d1f45b783d7b5951f84f14a2daf9a7f326312482", "message": "updated description for replicasGoal", "committedDate": "2020-03-23T17:06:49Z", "type": "commit"}]}